ubuntu has package installer - apt
centos has package installer - yum

first do sudo apt update

Update - the links/references of these packages are updated
upgrade - new packages are installed

to install something - sudo apt install brave

to uninstall something - sudo apt uninstall/remove


sudo apt update - this needs superuser sudo
update updates the links/references to the packages  so that it can be installed

sudo apt upgrade - this installs the new packages,actual installation happens here



